    <p>Let us know if you need any special arrangements that differ from the terms below.</p>

    <h2>Prices</h2>
    <p>
      All orders are shipped at prices prevailing at time of shipment. In case of any substantial
      increase in price, we will notify you prior to shipment. Prices are FOB our Doral, Florida
      headquarters or our Atlanta, Georgia warehouse unless otherwise indicated.
      <span class="text-muted">(Updated to match our current HQ address — verify this still matches your shipping terms before publishing.)</span>
      Export packing, crating, and special handling are charged at cost plus 10%.
    </p>

    <h2>Terms</h2>
    <p>
      Standard terms are wire transfer or cash with order. Open accounts may be established for
      firms and individuals who have demonstrated they can pay accounts promptly and without delay;
      contact us for details before ordering on an open-account basis. Schools, colleges,
      institutions, and government agencies may place orders with a properly executed purchase order.
    </p>

    <h2>International Orders</h2>
    <p>
      We accept orders from anywhere in the world. Unless other payment arrangements are made, our
      terms are a confirmed, irrevocable letter of credit or bank wire transfer.
    </p>

    <h2>Photos</h2>
    <p>
      Photos are available for any item we have for sale for a $15 fee, deductible from the purchase
      price if you buy the item.
    </p>

    <h2>Returns and Credits</h2>
    <p>
      Merchandise cannot be returned for credit without prior written approval. A return request
      must be made within three days of receipt, and the returned shipment must be given to the
      carrier within 7 days of written return approval. Freight and insurance on returns must be
      prepaid by the purchaser regardless of reason. Merchandise sold as-is, clearance, or special
      clearance is final sale.
    </p>

    <h2>Restocking Fees</h2>
    <p>Merchandise returned with no defect found is subject to a 25% restocking fee.</p>

    <h2>Minimum Order</h2>
    <p>Our minimum order is $100.</p>

    <h2>C.O.D. Shipments</h2>
    <p>C.O.D. shipments are not permitted except by special arrangement.</p>

    <h2>Credit Card Orders</h2>
    <p>We accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, and Discover, subject to a service charge.</p>

    <h2>Payment and Collections</h2>
    <p>
      If collection proceedings are required, the buyer is responsible for our reasonable attorneys’
      fees and court costs, plus 1.5% per month (18% per annum) on unpaid principal balances in the
      event of default.
    </p>

